    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained farfalle</strong> to the <strong>squash & tomato sauce</strong> with the <strong>reserved pasta water</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Transfer the mixture to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p>",
