    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the pasta mixture with the <strong>roasted tomato wedges</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>torn mozzarella</strong> and <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> – this is your <strong>bats & cobwebs cheesy squash pasta bake</strong></p><p>Put the pasta bake in the oven for 10-12 min or until melted and golden</p>",
